Description: Methods for distance-based fuzzy unsupervised and
    semi-supervised clustering, including fuzzy and possibilistic models 
    based on alternating optimization (AO) algorithm.
    The package introduces a vectorized estimation
    framework for prototype-based fuzzy clustering algorithms,
    enabling modular algorithm design and extensibility.
    It also supports storage and retrieval of intermediate AO
    optimization results for downstream analysis and processing.
    For more details see Kmita et al. (2024) <doi:10.1109/TFUZZ.2024.3370768>.
